# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in your own token from
# chromatic.com -> your project -> Manage -> Configure.
# Note: .env.local is only read by the chromatic publish script. Keep real
# secrets out of any .env* file in this app dir anyway — Storybook <10.1.10
# bundled .env contents into built Storybooks (Dec 2025 advisory).
CHROMATIC_PROJECT_TOKEN=
